{
  "stem": "3804.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somebody else will speak with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You captured him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Good bye.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You hold him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Speaking?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "An interrogator will do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But that's a problem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I asked myself, why shouldn't I talk to him?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He's a criminal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He killed my-- he gave orders to kill my sister, children, and my relatives, and all this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "What's the big thing if I know how he did it?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "What is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's against the law?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Or it's against tradition?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Or it's against something, that you can't do it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's only, maybe, it will-- wouldn't-- it was not so good for the interrogation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But who cares, I said to myself?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] didn't like this man what the interrogation has.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But you know, he was really a German traditional and all this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In a way, it went-- it brought me to this, that he is a-- how do you say?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He reminded me a little bit of this German tradition.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I didn't like German tradition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I speak, and I question, and all this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I-- after we came into the room, and the question was, well, is he Eichmann, or not?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So we asked him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The first question was, the interrogator, what's your name?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So in German, he said, I'm Ricardo Klement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Again, what's your name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Ricardo Klement.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We felt, oy vey, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Didn't feel so good, even with it was not true, but--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, we undressed him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew that he has a-- the number under his arm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was erased.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was a mark there, erased.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We saw the-- I say, the accident.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We saw exactly where the accident was right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The number of the head was right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we asked him about the number of his-- number of his-- Gestapo number.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
